quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  101,1,The pounding disaster
  101,2,What is the pounding disaster
  101,3,And do you know what the pounding disaster is
  101,4,A day when the people become like scattered butterflies
  101,5,and the mountains become like fluffed up colored wool
  101,6,As for anyone whose balance (of good deeds) is heavy
  101,7,then he is in a pleasant life
  101,8,And as for anyone whose balance (of good deeds) is light
  101,9,then his residence is a bottomless pit
  101,10,And you don't even know what it is
  101,11,(It is) a scorching fire